								"editorData": [
									{
										"data": [
											{
												"key": {
													"type": 22,
													"value": "AnimationTags"
												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "[ChrisD] Player inserts the crest inside the pedestal to disarm the trap. Player slowly takes the mace with ease and examines it a bit."
												}
											},
											{
												"key": {
													"type": 22,
													"value": "Attitude"
												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "Default"
												}
											},
											{
												"key": {
													"type": 22,
													"value": "CinematicNodeContext"
												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "The crest clicks into place, floor hinges unlock, and the ring on the floor begins to spin.\r\n\r\nAny companions step back, and the player looks around in positive anticipation.\r\n\r\nThe floor ring slowly rises up as the four pillars also rise, the crystals they're topped with starting to glow warmly as if suffused with sunlight.\r\n\r\nThe still-spinning floor ring aligns with the gyro, and as it also begins to move and rotate a glow forms at its core.  - The gyro aligns its rings into a flat horizontal plane over the mace.  -  A shaft of light coming down around mace, as the gyro glow fades and the mace’s glow intensifies.\r\n\r\nThe mace unlocks from its rigid upright position and begins floating in the shaft of light in a slanted, bobbing, “take me” manner.\r\n\r\nThe player gently takes the mace as the other glows fade slightly, admiring the mace’s pulsing glow as companions step forward."
												}
											},
											{
												"key": {
													"type": 22,
													"value": "CinematicObjects"
												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": ""
												}
											},
